  "detailed_description": "Cross Numbers is crossword style, math based puzzle game. Numbers and operands are generated and hidden at random, and you have to complete the equations using the available tiles.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >RANDOMLY GENERATED</h2>Puzzles are generated at random, meaning every game is unique.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1633750/extras/143fa6f54cfe269bca433263d1781af2.poster.avif?t=1741007421\" width=614 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1633750/extras/143fa6f54cfe269bca433263d1781af2.webm?t=1741007421\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SHARE WITH FRIENDS</h2>Want to solve puzzles with your friends? Share your favourite seeds with your friends to see if they can complete it faster than you.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1633750/extras/bdd09114a682d066bcd79abd44012d11.apng?t=1741007421\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1633750/extras/bdd09114a682d066bcd79abd44012d11.poster.avif?t=1741007421\" class=\"bb_img\" width=614 height=194 /></picture></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CUSTOMISABLE THEMES</h2>Don't like how the game looks? Use one of the included presets or change the theme to your exact liking.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1633750/extras/3983c76998f324bf7c928dc63b1abe06.poster.avif?t=1741007421\" width=614 height=410 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1633750/extras/3983c76998f324bf7c928dc63b1abe06.webm?t=1741007421\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>",
